 USE
 This sketch takes an image and uses text for pixels. Nuff said.

 - Arrow keys UP & DOWN - changes pixel grid resolution.
 - Arrow keys RIGHT & LEFT - changes font size.
 - key 1 activates/deactivates random glyph selector
 - key s for exporting hi-res images [ once export is finished, program exits ].

